text: The Governor has gone from “flatten the curve,” to “testing, tracing and trends,” to today: “feelings.” Without real, complete data he is running out of reasons to justify the continued shut down of our economy and people’s livelihoods. #COVID19 #releasethedata https://t.co/bXUU8qVGo1
